import React from 'react'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import CalendarWithExercises from '../components/CalendarWithExercises'
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Container from '@mui/material/Container';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import { useContext } from 'react'
import { UserContext } from '../App';
import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom';

const Routine = (props) => {

    const {allRoutines} = useContext(UserContext)

    const location = useLocation();
    console.log(location.state.index)

  return (
    <>
        <Navbar/>
        <Container maxWidth="1600" 
    sx={{
      display: 'flex',
      flexDirection: 'column',
      height: 'auto',
    }}>
      <Box sx={{ 
        padding: '1em',
        display: 'flex',
      flexDirection: 'column',
      alignItems: 'center',
      width: 'auto',
      marginTop: '5em'
        }}>
          <Typography variant='h2'>
               SCHEDULE YOUR TRAINING PLAN
          </Typography>

               <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'row',
                   justifyContent: 'space-around', width: '100%',
                   backgroundColor: '#bdb9b7', borderRadius: '15px',
                   padding: '1.5em 1em 1.5em 1em', marginBottom: '4em'}}>

            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'monday'} indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'tuesday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'wednesday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'thursday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'friday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'saturday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'sunday'}  indexOfRoutine={location.state.index}/>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    </Container>
         <Footer/>
    </>
    )
}

export default Routine
